hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.util

Class Func2Builder<T,U,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.util.Func2Builder<T,U,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the function first parameter type
    U - the function second parameter type
    V - the return type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Func2<T,U,V>

    public class Func2Builder<T,U,V>
extends Object
implements Func2<T,U,V>
    Class holding a Func2 object and providing various relevant methods of the Functions utility class as instance methods.

    The class itself is of type Func2<T, U, V> and can be used where this type is needed.

    Since:
    0.96.1
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2012.02.02.
